Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.14,0:00:06.65,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}敵の意志をくじく！ 戦う意志を
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.14,0:00:06.65,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}By using...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.65,0:00:10.65,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}立ち上がる意志を あらがう意志を
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.65,0:00:10.65,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}words?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.14,0:00:14.62,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}悟らせてやろう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.14,0:00:14.62,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}King...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.62,0:00:21.13,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}お前の努力と自信 いかに無意味なものかをな！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.62,0:00:21.13,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Would you like to know your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.60,0:03:38.61,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}勘で俺が爆破しないと 判断したか？ いや　あの顔は違う！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.60,0:03:38.61,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Centipede x And x Memory
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.61,0:03:49.12,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}自分の爆発で やけどをしないんだろう)) ((簡単よ　爆発の攻撃力より 大きいオーラで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.61,0:03:49.12,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}As the King and Netero prepared \Nfor their final battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.11,0:04:25.14,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}((うん　２回目はビスケのオーラが 少なくなった)) ) ((その違いを感じ取れれば 奴との戦いが少しだけ楽よ))
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.11,0:04:25.14,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Beneath the palace, Ikalgo was still sobbing, having failed to finish off \Nthe unconscious Brovada.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.10,0:05:17.61,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}腕や足なら表皮は焼け 神経や筋肉に重大な障害が残る。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.10,0:05:17.61,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Fire! This is the best option!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.61,0:05:21.16,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}指なら跡形もなく消し飛ぶだろう。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.61,0:05:21.16,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}There's no one else to help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.16,0:05:27.10,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}お前が俺の「凝」での攻撃を　全て 「凝」でガードするのは不可能。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.16,0:05:27.10,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I h-have to... kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.10,0:05:34.12,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}できれば　これ以上　やりたくない 戦ってみて　よく分かった。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.10,0:05:34.12,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}This is no time to be crying...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.12,0:05:39.63,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}お前には才能があり　未来があり 次のチャンスもある。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.12,0:05:39.63,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I have to find Palm! Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.63,0:05:45.18,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}意地だけで　その全てを捨てるのは あまりに無意味だと思わないか？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.63,0:05:45.18,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The door to the warehouse area is open. So is the door leading to the garage!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.18,0:05:49.12,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}さっさと諦めろ このクソガキが！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.18,0:05:49.12,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Why? Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.12,0:05:55.11,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}((もしも奴が　両手を爆発に 使うようなそぶりを見せたら もう赤信号よ))
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.12,0:05:55.11,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If you move, I'll attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.11,0:05:58.60,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}((何をおいても 作戦実行にのみ集中すること))
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.11,0:05:58.60,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Welfin...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.60,0:06:04.69,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ごめん　ビスケ　キルア ここから先は　俺のわがまま
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.60,0:06:04.69,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I have a lot of things to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.69,0:06:07.12,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}試さないと気が済まないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.69,0:06:07.12,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If you seem to be trying anything funny, I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.12,0:06:11.11,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}だって 思いついちゃったから！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.12,0:06:11.11,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}What he wants to ask me
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.11,0:06:18.10,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}もし　本当に そう思っているなら お前が降りろ！　ゲンスルー！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.11,0:06:18.10,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}is obvious! The number of my allies, their roles, and their abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.10,0:06:22.10,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}残念だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.10,0:06:22.10,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}And he intends to use any means \Nnecessary to get the answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.21,0:06:30.09,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}教えてやろう。 世の中には死ぬより つらいことなど
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.21,0:06:30.09,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}People could die if I leak information.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.09,0:06:35.62,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}いくらでもあるとな！ 両腕を同時に爆破する。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.09,0:06:35.62,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If he's a Manipulator, he can obtain the information against my will.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.62,0:06:38.62,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}無事に残しておきたいほうを 「凝」で守れ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.62,0:06:38.62,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.62,0:06:43.14,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}その次に残ったほうの腕と左足を 同時に爆破する。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.62,0:06:43.14,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}D-Don't move! I really will kill you! Go ahead... Kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.14,0:06:50.62,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}残したいほうを「凝」で守れ それを延々と続ける。 手足がなくなるまでな。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.14,0:06:50.62,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That's what I want! Stop! If the alternative is betraying my buddies, I'll take you with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.62,0:06:54.60,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}やれるもんならやってみろ！ では。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.62,0:06:54.60,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Ouch! Bastard! Now you've done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.12,0:06:59.62,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}くらえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.12,0:06:59.62,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Missile Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.70,0:07:11.70,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}くっ…　な…　何が起きた？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.70,0:07:11.70,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'm... not dead... I didn't sustain any damage. What was that attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.12,0:07:22.11,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}血？　ダメージ？ 俺が攻撃されたのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.12,0:07:22.11,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Damn, that hurts... You little punk... Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.11,0:07:29.14,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}最初は　グ！ ヤバい！　動け！ よけるんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.11,0:07:29.14,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That bastard... How did a wimp like \Nthat figure out my weakness?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.14,0:07:32.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ジャン！　ケン！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.14,0:07:32.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Missile Man requires questions and answers to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.71,0:07:35.21,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}グ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.71,0:07:35.21,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If an enemy attacks before I can ask \Na question, it's null and void!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.11,0:07:41.62,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}く…　うっ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.11,0:07:41.62,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The wound isn't deep... I'll take my time beating him to a pulp.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.60,0:07:50.60,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}何だ？　今のは　何が起きた？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.60,0:07:50.60,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.12,0:08:07.12,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}くっ！　こいつ… 左右の手でダメージが違う！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.12,0:08:07.12,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He planted something inside me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.12,0:08:09.61,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}おそらく左手は完全に捨てて
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.12,0:08:09.61,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Those were created by my Nen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.61,0:08:12.65,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}右手を 攻防力３０程度のオーラで覆い
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.61,0:08:12.65,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}They're black centipedes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.65,0:08:20.62,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}残りの攻防力７０を 足に集中させて… 俺を攻撃した！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.65,0:08:20.62,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}They grow by feeding on your resistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.61,0:08:41.63,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それを両手同時に消費すれば 他の箇所のオーラは 極度に少なくなる そこを突かれた！ しかし… 考えついても普通やるか？ ひと泡　吹かせてやったぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.61,0:08:41.63,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If you disobey my orders or try to hurt me, you'll suffer excruciating pain, then they'll tear your body apart and you'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.10,0:08:52.10,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}けど…　動くぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.10,0:08:52.10,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Wh-What are you doing, fool? Weren't you listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.65,0:08:59.11,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}もう…　いいや。 「もういい」？　諦めたか？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.65,0:08:59.11,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If you try to do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.11,0:09:08.59,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}左手は吹き飛ばされて 右手も重傷 俺への反撃も決まり 一矢報いた
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.11,0:09:08.59,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That's fine with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.59,0:09:11.12,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}十分　満足したはず
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.59,0:09:11.12,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If my life is all it takes, I'll give it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.66,0:09:19.66,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ここからが本番だ 行くぞ　ゲンスルー！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.66,0:09:19.66,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}S-Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.60,0:09:25.60,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}イカれてやがる！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.60,0:09:25.60,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}No, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.08,0:09:40.17,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ブック！ カード？　特に 警戒するものは　なかったはず
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.08,0:09:40.17,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Now, it'll take no time for the black centipedes \Nto grow large enough to kill him instantly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.17,0:09:46.60,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}カードが変身… 「聖騎士の首飾り」か！ 一体　何をする気だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.17,0:09:46.60,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Don't worry. I'm not interested in killing you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.60,0:09:54.61,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}諦めるなら　今のうちだぞ。 これを使うと　最悪の場合 お前は　死ぬかもしれない。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.60,0:09:54.61,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I just need to make sure that you can't leave. I still...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.57,0:10:00.14,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}だが　待てよ… これは　チャンスだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.57,0:10:00.14,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}have plenty of bullets.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.14,0:10:02.20,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ブック。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.14,0:10:02.20,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Bastard! Don't mess with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.20,0:10:04.58,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}根負けだ　どうやっても
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.20,0:10:04.58,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.58,0:10:07.59,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}お前に参ったと 言わせるのは　無理なようだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.58,0:10:07.59,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You're dead! I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.58,0:10:36.10,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}チッ！　２撃目は 「凝」でガードされたか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.58,0:10:36.10,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It's so easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.58,0:10:50.14,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}もう　これで　こいつは 「ブック」も「ゲイン」も唱えられない！ ゲンスルー お前は　一番 やっちゃいけないことをした
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.58,0:10:50.14,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}When I'm prepared to offer my own life, it's so easy to pull the trigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.10,0:11:31.15,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}その触れた箇所に　爆弾を 仕掛けることができる能力だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.10,0:11:31.15,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I g-get it... I get it, already.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.15,0:11:35.11,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}爆弾を解除するためには 俺の体に触れて
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.15,0:11:35.11,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I won't go anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.11,0:11:38.59,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「ボマー捕まえた」と 言わねばならない。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.11,0:11:38.59,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I surrender. Please... Don't fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.58,0:11:45.10,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}お前の「念」で 防ぎ切れるレベルじゃないぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.58,0:11:45.10,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The pain is going away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.10,0:11:48.60,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}これで　発動条件は整った。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.10,0:11:48.60,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The creatures inside me are suffering?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.60,0:11:53.59,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}お前に触れて「ボマー」と言えば 自動的に爆弾は　スタートする。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.60,0:11:53.59,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I lose, damn it... I can't move anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.59,0:12:00.10,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}せいぜい逃げてみろ。 そんな余力があればな。 条件が整ったのは
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.59,0:12:00.10,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Is it because Welfin admitted defeat?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.10,0:12:06.10,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}最初は　グ…。 うっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.10,0:12:06.10,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Man, I knew it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.10,0:12:10.66,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}これだ　さっきのだ 踏み込めば　やられる！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.10,0:12:10.66,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I had a feeling this would happen eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.66,0:12:13.09,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}近寄らせない気か!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.66,0:12:13.09,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.09,0:12:16.08,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ジャン！　ケン！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.09,0:12:16.08,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I didn't think I was this weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.08,0:12:19.08,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}グ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.08,0:12:19.08,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I didn't think it'd be so scary \Nto face someone who fights
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.09,0:12:30.61,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あっ！　落とし穴!! しかし　奴も落ちてるぞ!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.09,0:12:30.61,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}What? The pain has stopped, but can \Nyou get rid of these bugs?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.61,0:12:45.09,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}高い…　とても登れん！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.61,0:12:45.09,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.09,0:12:49.08,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}だが　それは　奴も同じはず この状況じゃ 追い詰められたのは
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.09,0:12:49.08,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Give me a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.08,0:12:51.58,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}逆に奴のほうじゃないか！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.08,0:12:51.58,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I don't have a way to deactivate Missile Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.64,0:12:56.67,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}いない!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.64,0:12:56.67,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But if I tell the truth, I'm in real trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.67,0:13:00.11,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ゲンスルー…。 なっ…！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.67,0:13:00.11,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Damn, how do I get out of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.59,0:13:05.60,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}カードは　バインダーから出して １分経つと
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.59,0:13:05.60,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I need to buy time...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.60,0:13:08.10,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}アイテムに戻る！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.60,0:13:08.10,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Until I can come up with a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.12,0:13:15.62,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}岩!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.12,0:13:15.62,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The pain is making me... feel faint...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.60,0:13:39.58,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.60,0:13:39.58,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Wait! Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.58,0:13:42.58,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ジャン！　ケン！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.58,0:13:42.58,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I was lying! I won't do it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.58,0:13:45.10,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ま…　待て！　参った!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.58,0:13:45.10,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Then get rid of these.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.10,0:13:47.09,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}参った!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.10,0:13:47.09,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yeah, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.09,0:13:50.07,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}グ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.09,0:13:50.07,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}So, the thing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.58,0:14:02.58,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ふぅ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.58,0:14:02.58,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I can't remove them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.59,0:14:06.09,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}オス!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.59,0:14:06.09,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Not once they've been activated!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.08,0:14:15.62,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}気づいたか？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.08,0:14:15.62,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'm not trying to trick you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.62,0:14:18.67,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}早速だけど　バインダー出して。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.62,0:14:18.67,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The insects are in pain again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.67,0:14:21.59,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あんた達が仲間を裏切って 手にしたカード
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.67,0:14:21.59,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Maybe because Welfin is telling the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.59,0:14:24.11,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}全部　返してもらうわさ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.59,0:14:24.11,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Can you really blame me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.11,0:14:32.08,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}条件がある。 「大天使」で バラを治してやってくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.11,0:14:32.08,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I only use this attack when I want to kill someone. I never cared what happened after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.08,0:14:35.09,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「クローン」は　ある。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.08,0:14:35.09,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I never gave any thought to \Nwhat happened to my enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.09,0:14:41.59,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}安心しろよ　初めっから そのつもりだから。 こっちは　あらかじめ ６人分の「クローン」を
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.09,0:14:41.59,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Nen abilities are really something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.59,0:14:43.59,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}用意してたわさ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.59,0:14:43.59,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}My abilities reflect my own personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.60,0:14:49.60,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ブック。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.60,0:14:49.60,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}My personality? His true intentions?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.58,0:15:06.58,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}わらわに　何を望む？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.58,0:15:06.58,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I once knew someone just like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.58,0:15:11.59,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}こいつの両手と喉を元通りに 治してもらいたいんだけど。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.58,0:15:11.59,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Do you have any memories from \Nwhen you were human?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.59,0:15:14.59,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あっ　つうか できれば悪いとこ全部。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.59,0:15:14.59,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Wh-Why are you asking about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.59,0:15:16.61,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}お安いご用。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.59,0:15:16.61,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I can't remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.61,0:15:23.16,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}では　その者の体 治してしんぜよう。 フ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.61,0:15:23.16,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You're lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.10,0:15:32.09,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あ…。 あっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.10,0:15:32.09,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If you don't tell me the truth, I'll shoot you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.60,0:15:44.60,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}はい　もう１枚　予備の「大天使」。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.60,0:15:44.60,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}When I woke up, my first thought was...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.60,0:16:01.61,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}次は　キルアね。 ゲンスルー　あんたのバインダー 使わせてもらうわよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.60,0:16:01.61,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I can still remember it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.19,0:16:12.10,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「大天使の息吹」は カード化限度枚数がＭＡＸです。 「クローン」は　破壊されます。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.19,0:16:12.10,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'm sure those monster bugs killed me in NGL.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.09,0:16:30.58,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「大天使の息吹」の 引換券を増やしたんだ。 今頃は　あっちの引換券が２枚 「大天使」になってるよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.09,0:16:30.58,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I was fed to the Queen, \Nand reborn as something new...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.60,0:16:42.09,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}他のプレーヤーがあなたに対し 「コンタクト」を使用しました。 よう！　ゴレイヌだ。 どうやら　勝ったようだな。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.60,0:16:42.09,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But I still... I still remember the one thing \NI most wanted to forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.58,0:16:51.07,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}納得いかねえ。 こんな人殺しの連中に 「大天使」を使うのなら トレードは断る。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.58,0:16:51.07,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The sight of my father strangling me, and the woman watching behind him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.07,0:17:00.08,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺も　殺し屋だぜ。 え？ こいつら以上に　人を殺してる。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.07,0:17:00.08,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}At first, I only had flashbacks of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.08,0:17:04.58,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}このゲームには　みんな 大なり小なり　命を懸けて来てる。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.08,0:17:04.58,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Over time, I remembered the \Nentire sequence of events.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.12,0:17:09.17,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺が殺して来たのは
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.12,0:17:09.17,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I was saved by...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.17,0:17:15.10,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そんな覚悟から 程遠い所にいた人ばかり。 俺のほうが　よっぽど たち悪いだろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.17,0:17:15.10,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}my little brother, who was unrelated by blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.10,0:17:18.58,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}いや お前と　こいつらとは違う。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.10,0:17:18.58,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I remember now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.58,0:17:24.10,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺は　お前を気に入っているが こいつらのことは大嫌いだ！ それ　理屈になってねえよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.58,0:17:24.10,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He looked just like Gyro!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.11,0:17:29.14,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}お前らだって　同じだろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.11,0:17:29.14,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You know. The king!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.18,0:17:35.08,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}私達は　彼らを 見殺しにしていいとは考えません。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.18,0:17:35.08,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We used to brag about whose \Nlife was more miserable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.08,0:17:41.09,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}戦う時は　お互い命懸けだし 相手を殺すくらいの覚悟で 臨みます。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.08,0:17:41.09,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He was the only one I could \Nturn to when I needed
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.09,0:17:45.11,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}でも　勝負がついたら その先は　話が違います。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.09,0:17:45.11,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}to laugh away my tears...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.11,0:17:49.10,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺だって　ゲンスルーが 大勢のプレーヤーを殺したこと
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.11,0:17:49.10,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We were both empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.10,0:17:54.18,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}許してないよ。 でも　戦う前に３人で決めたんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.10,0:17:54.18,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}So we had nothing to hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.18,0:18:01.09,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「クローン」は ６枚　用意しておこうって。 その時の会話の流れは よく覚えてないけど。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.18,0:18:01.09,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I wonder what he's doing now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.60,0:18:14.65,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}勝負がついて 「大天使の息吹」が手に入ったら 誰がケガしても治そうって。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.60,0:18:14.65,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I want to see him one more time...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.64,0:18:40.60,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}事情が変わって 「クローン」が使えなくなった。 「大天使」は　あと１枚しかない。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.64,0:18:40.60,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yes, I just want to see Gyro.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.60,0:18:50.59,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あと１枚って お前ら　それ　オリジナルだろ！ 俺は平気だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.60,0:18:50.59,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'm tired of dealing with Ants and humans, with money and nations...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.16,0:18:57.20,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.16,0:18:57.20,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The bugs are gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.20,0:19:00.10,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}んじゃ　このまま「アカンパニー」で マサドラ行くか！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.20,0:19:00.10,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You still have something to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.60,0:19:06.59,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}おい　待てよ！ 分かった　お前らにやるよ！ 「大天使の息吹」。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.60,0:19:06.59,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Why did you open the doors?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.59,0:19:12.58,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}えっ？ えっ　いいの？　ホントに？ ああ　つうか ここに来て話を聞く前は
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.59,0:19:12.58,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Oh, I was letting those weaklings \Nreach the treasure in the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.63,0:19:19.60,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「大天使」だけじゃなく 俺達のカード　全部な。 えっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.63,0:19:19.60,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}They can't put up much of a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.60,0:19:23.09,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}これは　ツェズゲラ含め 俺達５人　全員の合意だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.60,0:19:23.09,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I was watching you and Bro on the monitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.09,0:19:27.11,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺達は　もうゲームを降りたんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.09,0:19:27.11,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}And I told them to pass while \Nyou were on the way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.17,0:19:41.09,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ああ　ツェズゲラ達に 違約金を払う形でな。 俺も４０億で手を打ったよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.17,0:19:41.09,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}A coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.09,0:19:45.11,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}４０億!? ちょっと！ それ　少し　よこしなさいよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.09,0:19:45.11,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It was that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.11,0:19:55.16,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}何　言ってんだよ！ ４人で　１０億ずつ 分けるに決まってんだろ。 え！ 当然だろう。 これは　俺１人の力じゃ　ない。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.11,0:19:55.16,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Once I saw that you couldn't finish Bro, I couldn't have been more wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.59,0:20:02.60,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あんたって奴は…。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.59,0:20:02.60,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.60,0:20:05.60,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}なんて　いい奴なんだわさ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.60,0:20:05.60,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'm too tired to move...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.60,0:20:11.61,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}とにかく　このカードは 全て　お前達にやる。 条件は　たった一つ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.60,0:20:11.61,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I have one last question. Did you see a woman in the palace?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.61,0:20:14.62,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}必ず　お前らが 最初にクリアすること。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.61,0:20:14.62,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}A woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.62,0:20:20.08,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うん！ 問題なし。 これで 指定ポケットカードは９９枚。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.62,0:20:20.08,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Not sure if it's the one you're talking about, but the Royal Guard captured a human, \Nand put her in a cocoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.08,0:20:23.08,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}残るは ナンバー０　のみってわけだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.08,0:20:23.08,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.08,0:20:26.08,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}残り１枚…。 あぁ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.08,0:20:26.08,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Take the elevator up, then turn left.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.10,0:20:32.09,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}９７　９８…。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.10,0:20:32.09,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It's the room at the end of the hall. They called it #1.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.09,0:20:35.11,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そして　これが
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.09,0:20:35.11,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.59,0:20:48.59,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}プレーヤーの方々に お知らせです。 たった今　あるプレーヤーが
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.59,0:20:48.59,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Telling the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.59,0:20:52.10,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}９９種の指定ポケットカードを そろえました。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.59,0:20:52.10,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}feels really good...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.10,0:21:02.59,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それを記念いたしまして 今から１０分後に 『グリードアイランド』内にいる プレーヤー全員参加の クイズ大会を開始いたします。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.10,0:21:02.59,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Welfin had spent his life unable \Nto trust himself or others.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.08,0:21:08.60,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}指定ポケットカードに関する 問題です。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.08,0:21:08.60,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Telling Ikalgo the location of \Nthe one he searched for
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.60,0:21:13.08,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}正解率の最も高かった プレーヤーに賞品としまして
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.60,0:21:13.08,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}was the first time he'd opened \Nup and spoken honestly.
